</ul>
<p>In this context, continuation of the internecine warfare would have created hurdles. In this context, the rise of Islam helped people come together. Prophet Muhammad produced a new sect called Islam &#8211; total surrender to one God (tawhid, monotheism) &#8211; with one of the objectives to create brotherhood and keep unity in tribal regions.</p>
