<p>Thus, interpretations of Rousseau&#8217;s ideas can vary, and his work has been used to support a wide range of political viewpoints over time.</p>
<h2>Social Contract: Additional Information</h2>
<p>The doctrine that the state originated in a contract was a favourite home of political speculation during the 17<sup>th</sup>-18<sup>th</sup> centuries. All thinkers agree that <u>some sort of social contract is necessary to create a civil society.</u></p>
